Value: Nuheara Limited, a wearables technology company, engages in the development and commercialization of hearing and wearables technology platforms worldwide. The company offers IQbuds2 MAX, a hearing bud and related accessories; IQstream TV to control volume levels; IQbuds BOOST accessories; and Bluetooth transmitters. It sells its products through traditional retail and direct-to-consumer online sales platform. The company is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
